## TrimFlex Technology

TrimFlex represents our most advanced line of flexible emblems, designed to conform to curved and complex surfaces without compromising visual quality.

### Key Features

- **Precision micro-injection** — ±0.05mm tolerances for exceptional detail
- **UV resistance** — maintains brilliance and color for over 10 years outdoors
- **3M VHB adhesive** — permanent bonding to any surface

### Manufacturing Process

Each TrimFlex emblem goes through a 12-stage process including injection molding, galvanic chrome plating, and automated quality control with machine vision.
